<item>
            <title>[LU-9331] liblnetconfig.a not installing properly with &quot;make install&quot;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9331</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When I do a &quot;make install&quot; from my Lustre source directory, the library liblnetconfig.a is not being properly installed. &#160;What is being installed in /lib does not match what is in the&#160;lnet/utils/lnetconfig/.libs directory. &#160;I&apos;m not really sure where the library which is installed comes from.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="45464">LU-9331</key>
