                            <comment id="194144" author="eberglan" created="Tue, 2 May 2017 13:57:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thought was part of PFL, Joe G indicated that it was not. &#160;Removed link from PFL tracking ticket&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="191901" author="doug" created="Thu, 13 Apr 2017 17:11:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Related to this is the fact that the utility lnetctl itself is also not being updated properly with &quot;make install&quot;. &#160;I have noticed that lnetctl is being rebuild under&#160;lnet/utils, but is not being copied to&#160;lnet/utils/.libs. &#160;The version in&#160;lnet/utils/.libs is what gets installed into /lib.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
